text: "Innocent" is a 2000 song by American hard rock band Fuel. It is the second single from their second studio album Something Like Human. It did not chart on the Billboard Top 100 but when to #4 on the Alternative Airplay chart and #10 on the Mainstream Rock chart. ==Track listing== Song written by Carl Bell ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:Alternative rock songs Category:Fuel (band) songs
title: Innocent (Fuel song)
